<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>문화창작동아리</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        
        .container {
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: white;
            height: 100vh;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .ghost-icon {
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
        }
        
        .sidebar {
            width: 70px;
            height: calc(100vh - 50px);
            background-color: white;
            border-right: 1px solid #eee;
            float: left;
        }
        
        .sidebar-menu {
            list-style: none;
        }
        
        .sidebar-menu li {
            padding: 15px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f5f5f5;
        }
        
        .sidebar-icon {
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .sidebar-label {
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        .content {
            margin-left: 70px;
            padding: 15px;
        }
        
        .content-header {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .post {
            border: 1px solid #eee;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 15px;
        }
        
        .post-title {
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .post-content {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .post-date {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
            text-align: right;
        }

        /* 구글 로그인 버튼 스타일 */
        .google-login-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4285F4;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>문화 창작동아리</h1>
            <div class="ghost-icon">👻</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="sidebar">
            <ul class="sidebar-menu">
                <li>
                  <a href="/index" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit; font-weight: bold;">
                    <span class="sidebar-icon">🏠</span>
                    <span class="sidebar-label">홈</span>
                  </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <a href="/calendar" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
                    <span class="sidebar-icon">📅</span>
                    <span class="sidebar-label">캘린더</span>
                  </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="/museum" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
                    <span class="sidebar-icon">🏛️</span>
                    <span class="sidebar-label">박물관</span></a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="http://127.0.0.1:3000/member" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
                    <span class="sidebar-icon">👤</span>
                    <span class="sidebar-label">멤버</span></a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="sidebar-icon">🔥</span>
                    <span class="sidebar-label">이벤트</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="sidebar-icon">🔖</span>
                    <span class="sidebar-label">북마크</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="sidebar-icon">🔔</span>
                    <span class="sidebar-label">알림</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="sidebar-icon">💬</span>
                    <span class="sidebar-label">기타</span>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="content-header">
                <h2>여기에 콘텐츠</h2>
            </div>
            
            <div class="post">
                <div class="post-title">공지사항</div>
                <div class="post-content">
                    이곳에 게시글 내용이 표시됩니다.
                </div>
                <div class="post-date">2025.3.8</div>
            </div>

            <!-- 구글 로그인 버튼 -->
            <a href="/auth/google" class="google-login-btn">구글로 로그인</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
